  "aboutSectionOffline": "Offline",
  "aboutOfflineBody": "Offline-first: after a successful load, the market list and full coin card (price, 24h change, description) are stored in a local SQLite database. Without a network you still see that saved data. The price chart is not cached—it is fetched only when online. A banner above the bottom navigation appears when the device reports no connection.",
  "aboutSectionData": "Data",
  "aboutSectionNetworking": "Networking",
  "aboutNetworkingBody": "Dio HTTP client with Retrofit-generated REST API interface (core/network/rest). The REST client is injected through an abstraction, following clean architecture principles.",
  "aboutDataBody": "CoinGecko public REST API (rate limits apply): market list and per-coin details (REST paths under /coins/…), plus market_chart time series for the USD price graph (periods from 1D to MAX).",
